data.description: Welcome to this beautiful new 4 bed 2 bath home in the heart of Winter Haven. Once you enter the home, you'll appreciate the thoughtful ceramic tile in the hallway and great room off the open kitchen. The master suite offers a great space. All bedrooms include carpet. The kitchen island and open floor plan are perfect for entertaining. Stepping out the sliding door, you'll find an extended patio, perfect for cookouts with family and/or friends. Not to mention that you can enjoy the spectacular sunrises and sunsets next to fruit trees in the morning or in the afternoon. Also, resort style community pools and playground. This home in Lucerne Park Reserve is well located, being only 15 minutes from downtown Winter Haven and 5 minutes from US27. Book your appointment today.
